1 "ANCIENT CITY OF AURORA" AURORA~
Suggested level range: 15 - 35
 
Legend speaks of a mystical city isolated from all civilization by a 
magical barrier. This city, Aurora, can now be accessed through a portal
that was ripped through the barrier connecting it to the Realms.  Why 
