&wAll of the variables listed as "actor" - $n, e, m, s - will all show "you"
to the character doing the action, and show the appropriate variable to the
other characters in the room.
 
Neat little additions - $q = When added to the end of a word will show an "s"
to other characters in the room, and not the person doing the action, eg:
"$n eat$q the apple." would be:
