was banned and by who.  Number can be a class or race name, a site address
or you can use # followed by the ban number. WARN will toggle the warn flag
on a CURRENTLY banned site/class or race.
 
ALLOW site/race/class  <address/race/class>  removes a site, class or race
from the ban list.  This also can be allowed by using # syntax.
