1 AV AVATAR AVATARS~
An avatar is a character who has improved themselves as far as is mortally
possible - level 50. When a character reaches this level, they automatically
become an Avatar and this is announced across the entire realms.
Avatars enjoy many advantages. For example, the avatar can survive happily
without ever needing to eat or drink, though hunger and thirst do still affect
regeneration.  Avatars also do not gain or lose experience.
Note that an Avatar character is different from a supplicated Avatar mobile.
see: HELP SUPPLICATE.
 
Avatars have their own channel, AV. This channel is not changed by
chan +/- all, but by chan +/- AVATAR.  It may be used by typing
'av message' or ':message'.
~

