Aeons ago, dark elves emerged from the elven race that lived within the
realms' valley.  Shortly thereafter, the elves found themselves in great
distress - torn between those following a path of chaos, and those 
maintaining a life of righteousness.  A great, painful war broke out and
scattered destruction over the centuries.  Magicks of immense power flew
back and forth as each alignment fended for themselves; Many a brethren
slain.  The valley was left in turmoil, drenched in the flesh and blood of
the elven kind.
 
