1 'DECK OF MANY THINGS'~
There are a lot of rumors that abound about the Deck of Many Things. Some say
it is a device left over from the war against the darkness, others will argue
that it is a toy of the Gods and as such, a temperamental entity. One thing
is for certain, the Deck of Many Things, when encountered, should not be
attempted unless one is stout of heart. It is a magical device that speaks in
riddles and at times, speaks very clearly to the Gods of its wishes, leaving
the victim in the dark. Beware the Deck of Many Things - It can bring you to
great riches or plunge you into eternal blackness; The Gods are bound to
follow the ruling of the Deck, and the Deck accepts only those who possess
the courage to face it.
 
&YNOTE: If you are not fully equipped the immortal residing over the pull
has every right to deny you your chance.  This is a game of risk and must
be played as such.
