1 'MOUNT KROZLOY'~
To the far west and north of Darkhaven, past the Hills of Moria,
in the Kingdom of Juargan, lies the home of the Half-Orc Nation.
Mount Krozloy is a heavily fortified, and easily guarded natural
stronghold, where the Half-Orcs gather to plan for battle and
conquest. 
 
