Trance places your character in a trance-like state during which mana can
be rapidly regenerated.  Once you begin trancing you cannot engage in other
activities (or type other commands) or you will break the trance state.

While in the trance you will see your mana regenerate every few seconds
until you are at your maximum.
 
Trancing regenerates mana more rapidly than meditation.
 
See also:  MEDITATE
